  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "chapterTitle": "一滴水珠",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "927832_24_19389-19651",
          "range": "19389-19651",
          "rangeStart": 19389,
          "rangeEnd": 19651,
          "markText": "欢乐是过眼烟云，转瞬即逝，常常是虚幻的；而忧伤却是永恒的、令人得益的、始终不渝的。欢乐总像昙花一现，不，更像闪电破空，夹着隆隆雷声飞驰而过。忧伤却像那神秘莫测的星星，虽然发出的是幽幽的光，却是昼夜不熄的，它能引起你萦怀亲人，思念爱情，憧憬某种神秘玄奥的事物，也说不清究竟是想到了令人苦恼而又甜蜜的过去，还是想到了那诱人的，而且由于难以捉摸而令人既畏怯又向往的将来。忧伤像个明智的成年人，它已经存在千百万年了。欢乐则永远是童蒙稚年，天真烂漫，因为它在每个人的心灵中获得新生，年事越长，欢乐就越少，犹如花朵，林子越密，花就越少。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1718842994,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-20 08:23:14",
          "chapterUid": 24,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=19389&rangeEnd=19651",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=19389&rangeEnd=19651"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_11804-11888",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "11804-11888",
      "markText": "这一条生下来就是为了要和人类共同劳动、一起生活的狗，终于也没有明白人们为什么要打死它，它声音嘶哑地号着，最后跟人一样悲痛地叹了一口气，死了，好像是在可怜谁，或者责怪谁。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11804&rangeEnd=11888",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11804&rangeEnd=11888"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_21_1732-1800",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "1732-1800",
      "markText": "写作需要的是全副心灵，而不是趋附时尚，不应该在文学中寻求地位，而应该从中寻找自我。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1732&rangeEnd=1800",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1732&rangeEnd=1800"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_24_17274-17333",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "17274-17333",
      "markText": "一滴椭圆形的露珠，饱满凝重，垂挂在纤长瘦削的柳叶的尖梢上，重力引它下坠，它凝敛不动，像是害怕自己的坠落会毁坏这个世界。",
      "totalCount": 510,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=17274&rangeEnd=17333",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=17274&rangeEnd=17333"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_25_42414-42478",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "42414-42478",
      "markText": "卫兵队长和上气不接下气的看守朝着采石厂悬崖跑去，只听一声：“斯大林同志万岁！”紧接着严寒中传来了孤独的、没有回音、啪的一声枪响。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=42414&rangeEnd=42478",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=42414&rangeEnd=42478"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_970-1058",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "970-1058",
      "markText": "一种空灵自在的心境，不为任何俗念所累，几乎达到了无我的境界，对周围的世界只有皮相的感觉，视而不见，在这种罕有的内心宁静的时刻，你会感到自己是大千一叶，和生命之树却有一茎相连……",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=970&rangeEnd=1058",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=970&rangeEnd=1058"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_462-519",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "462-519",
      "markText": "在一生中，只要你的亲人们还没有像古老森林里年久岁深的老树那样沉重地折断并訇然扑地，你总会得到许多爱，也会去爱人……",
      "totalCount": 410,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=462&rangeEnd=519",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=462&rangeEnd=519"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_35_13330-13368",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "13330-13368",
      "markText": "我究竟在寻求什么呢？我为什么痛苦？由于什么原因？为了什么目的？我找不到回答。",
      "totalCount": 400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=13330&rangeEnd=13368",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=13330&rangeEnd=13368"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_1090-1187",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "1090-1187",
      "markText": "只要活着，他的记忆就兢兢业业地工作着，不仅记得住个人的大量往事，而且还会记住在生活交叉路口萍水相逢的人们，他们中间有的已经永远淹没在翻腾的人流旋涡里了，有的却成了始终同你休戚与共、心心相连的人。",
      "totalCount": 364,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1090&rangeEnd=1187",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1090&rangeEnd=1187"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_27060-27134",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "27060-27134",
      "markText": "人与人心灵上的沟通被破坏了，他们生活中缺少了主要的东西——劳动，因而没法团结起来。他们腻烦了，相互厌恶，于是不管他们的意愿如何，不满、怨恨越积越多。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=27060&rangeEnd=27134",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=27060&rangeEnd=27134"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_411-429",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "411-429",
      "markText": "我回故乡去很少是出于本意和自己乐意的",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=411&rangeEnd=429",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=411&rangeEnd=429"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_2933-2985",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "2933-2985",
      "markText": "爸爸仍跟以前一样，喝酒喝得分文不剩，按照流浪汉随心所欲的行事准则，到处胡来，根本不关心孩子们和家里的事。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2933&rangeEnd=2985",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2933&rangeEnd=2985"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_23879-23934",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "23879-23934",
      "markText": "严酷的冬天，寒风吹来不仅彻骨而且刺心，因而大家要养成一种习惯：出去解手必须很快，像鸟拉屎一样，几乎是边飞边拉。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=23879&rangeEnd=23934",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=23879&rangeEnd=23934"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_30_18456-18542",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "18456-18542",
      "markText": "整整一冬再加一春，乌鸦、喜鹊、狗和猫都大嚼雷鸟；一旦起风，干涸的池塘四岸的黑羽就纷纷扬扬起来，在楚什镇上空翻飞，遮蔽了晴空，火药的余烬和死灰好像都蒙住了太阳茫然若失的脸庞。",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927832&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=18456&rangeEnd=18542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/417327f05e2858417a1f291?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=18456&rangeEnd=18542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "927832_23_7894-7967",
